law.text:
The following organizational units and administrative bodies shall be governed by their respective substantive chapters as set out below:
Board of Directors for the Center for School Safety under KRS Chapter 158;
Council on Postsecondary Education under KRS Chapter 164;
Department of Education under KRS Chapters 156, 157, 158, 161, 163, and 167;
Education Professional Standards Board under KRS Chapter 161;
Kentucky Board of Education under KRS Chapters 156 and 157;
Kentucky Commission on Deaf and Hard of Hearing under KRS Chapter 163; and
Kentucky Educational Television under KRS Chapter 168.
